name: U-Socket Wall Outlet
description:
U-Socket Wall Outlets   - ACE 7169

U-Socket Whether at home, office or when we're traveling, we are always hunting for a wall outlet to plug our chargers or adapters into but there are never enough available outlets to charge all the devices.


Smart Design. Innovation meets Functionality. With the abundance of USB-dependent devices, the need for easier and more convenient ways to charge our devices is greater than ever. U-Socket has developed an innovative solution that leverages smart technology and design to meet today's technology dependent lifestyle.


Made in the USA. A quality product made right here in the USA ensures that your U-Socket is constructed with care and precision. Our workers test each and every U-Socket to the highest standards before they are shipped out.

name: 3-Outlet Surge Protector Tap
description:
3-Outlet Surge Protector Tap

Provide electrical equipment and USB devices with protection against power surges by plugging them into the 3-Outlet Surge Protector Tap. This power center connects directly into a wall socket to help keep your floor uncluttered.

Provides surge protection for USB and electrical devices
Cordless tap plugs directly into a wall outlet
3 outlets and 4 USB ports
VPR-600V surge rating and 1,300 joules rating
